
Overview of noun salvo

The noun salvo has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (1) salvo -- (an outburst resembling the discharge of firearms or the release of bombs)
2. (1) fusillade, salvo, volley, burst -- (rapid simultaneous discharge of firearms; "our fusillade from the left flank caught them by surprise")
3. salvo -- (a sudden outburst of cheers; "there was a salvo of approval")
